            (function(win, top){
                if ( /\bkeep_in_frame\b/.test(location.search) ) { return; }
                var tl = top.location;
                if( isInFrame() ) {
                    try {
                        document.domain = '1688.com';
                        tl.href = getLoginUrlTo( tl.href );
                    } catch(e) {
                        try { tl.reload(); }
                        catch(e) { }
                    }
                }

                function isInFrame() { return top != win; }
                
                function getLoginUrlTo(url) { 
                    var href = win.location.href.replace( /\bdone=[^&$]*&?/, '' )
                    href += (/\?/.test(href) ? '&' : '?') + 'done=' + encodeURIComponent(url);
                    return href;
                }
            })( window, window.top );

      <div class="toutiao-main">
        <div class="detail-info">
          <h1>早春微凉，宝宝穿衣切莫犯错</h1>
          <div class="article-info">
            <span>作者：</span>
                                                <a href="https://me.1688.com/toutiao/*xC-i2FIbMCxSvFHLvm74ZDlbcgTT.htm" target="_blank">ppp88116</a>
                    <i>优质写手</i>                                        <span class="split">|</span>
            <span> 评论：</span>
                19
            <span class="split">|</span>
            <span> 浏览：</span>
                5484
            <span class="split">|</span>
            <span id="publishtime">2018-03-28 14:01:12</span>
          </div>
          <div class="article-content" data-spm="a3-detail">
                         <p>　　早春天气乍暖还寒，面对时冷时热的天气，妈妈应该如何给宝宝穿衣呢?正所谓“春捂秋冻”，春季给宝宝穿衣服一定要注意保暖，特别是头、手、腹部等重点部位。另外，春节给宝宝穿衣一定要根据情况，注意随时增减。</p> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<p>　　做到“三暖二凉”</p> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<p><img src="https://cbu01.alicdn.com/img/ibank/2018/725/034/8585430527_1772625398.jpg?__r__=1522216597937" alt="4" width="673" height="673"><br><br>　　乍暖还寒的早春天，年轻的父母们要给孩子“捂”着点儿，可使稚嫩的身体适应这种冷暖气候的变化，有利于维护孩子恒定体温的调节，起到防寒保暖的作用。那什么是“三暖二凉”呢?</p> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<p>　　一是背暖。</p> 
<p><br>　　背部保持适度温暖利于宝宝体内阳气生发，可预防疾病，减少受凉感冒的机会。妈妈在给宝宝增减衣服之前，不妨摸摸宝宝的背部，如果有点湿湿热热的，那就适当给宝宝减点衣服，如果有点凉，就要赶紧给宝宝加衣服哦!</p> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<p>　　二是肚暖。</p> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<p><img src="https://cbu01.alicdn.com/img/ibank/2018/762/989/8595989267_1772625398.jpg?__r__=1522216606493" alt="4" width="675" height="675"><br><br>　　有些好动宝宝喜欢跑跑跳跳，衣服如果没有束好，大动作时很容易露出小肚肚。腹部保暖，最好给宝宝戴个棉肚兜，既能维护宝宝胃肠道的功能，促进对食物的消化吸收，又能防止肚子因受凉而引起的腹痛、腹泻等症状。</p> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<p>　　三是脚暖。</p> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<p><img src="https://cbu01.alicdn.com/img/ibank/2018/937/791/8558197739_1772625398.jpg?__r__=1522216616425" alt="3" width="675" height="675"><br><br>　　俗话说“凉从脚上起”，这是因为脚与上呼吸道黏膜有着密切的神经联系，再加上脚部皮下脂肪层薄，保温性能差，又远离心脏，血液循环较差，一旦脚部受凉就易引发感冒。注意宝宝脚部的保暖，特别是在室内玩耍时也不要光脚在地上跑。给宝宝穿上小棉袜，宝宝的小脚暖和了，才能保证一身温暖，抵御寒冷，防病保健康。</p> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<p>　　二凉”是指头部和心胸要凉。</p> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<p><img src="https://cbu01.alicdn.com/img/ibank/2018/751/474/8532474157_1772625398.jpg?__r__=1522216626080" alt="2" width="674" height="674"><br><br>　　孩子经由体表散发的热量，有1/3是由头部发散的，如果头部捂的过热，容易引起头晕头昏、烦躁不安。所以，在室内、风和日丽的天气，要保持头凉，才能使孩子神清气爽。心胸凉，是指给孩子上身穿的衣服不要过于厚重臃肿，以免胸部受压，影响正常的呼吸与心脏功能。</p> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<p>　　分年龄保暖更明智</p> 
<p><br>　　新生儿活动量少，因而外出时穿衣应该多加一件;而1岁以上的宝宝经常跑跑跳跳，容易出汗，穿衣不宜过多过厚。所以宝宝保暖不应是一味地多穿一点，分年龄保暖更科学明智哦!</p> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<p>&nbsp;</p>

<script>
// 精华推荐
  function getRecommend(){
    // 获取数据
    jQuery.ajax({
      type: 'get',
      url: '//widget.1688.com/front/getJsonComponent.json',
      data: {
        namespace: 'queryRecommendArticles',
        widgetId: 'queryRecommendArticles',
        methodName: 'execute',
        bizType: 'alitop',
        filterName: 'recType',
        filterValue: 'BEST_ARTICLE',
        length: 1
      },
      dataType: 'jsonp',
    }).then(function(result){
  		if(result && !result.hasError){
  			var dataList = result.content['dataList'];
  			if( dataList && result.content.success ){
  				if( dataList[0] ){
  					var obj = dataList[0];
  					var aElement = jQuery('#toutiao-recommend a');
  					aElement.attr('href', '//toutiao.1688.com/article/' + obj['id'] + '.htm');
  					aElement.attr('title', obj['title']);
  					
                                        jQuery('#toutiao-recommend p').html( obj['title'] );

  					aElement.find('img').attr('src', obj['thumbnailPic']);
  					return;
  				}
  			}
    		
  		}
  		jQuery('#toutiao-recommend').hide();
    })
  }
  getRecommend();
</script>

<script>
function getStrategy(){
  // 获取数据
  jQuery.ajax({
    type: 'get',
    url: '//widget.1688.com/front/getJsonComponent.json',
    data: {
      namespace: 'queryRecommendArticles',
      widgetId: 'queryRecommendArticles',
      methodName: 'execute',
      bizType: 'alitop',
      filterName: 'recType',
      filterValue: 'TIPS_ARTICLE',
      length: 5
    },
    dataType: 'jsonp',
  }).then(function(result){
  	if(result && !result.hasError){
  		var dataList = result.content['dataList'];
  		if( dataList && result.content.success ){
  			var html = '';
  			for(var i = 0, len = dataList.length; i < len; i++){
  				var obj = dataList[i];
  				html += '<li>'
                      +'<a href="//toutiao.1688.com/article/' + obj['id'] + '.htm" title="'+obj['title']+'" target="_blank">'+obj['title']+'</a>'
                    +'</li>';
  			}

            var listElement = jQuery('#strategy-list');
       		listElement.html( html );
  			return;
        }
    }
  	jQuery('.toutiao-strategy').hide();
  })
}
getStrategy();
</script>

<script>
fmd.config({
    hasStamp: true
});
define([
  'jquery',
  'util/template/2.0',
  'app/alitop/js/global/helper'
  ], function(jQuery, Template, Helper){
    Template.helper('fommatPublishTime', Helper.formatTime );

    function logAboutRecord( articleId ){
      // 点击打点
      jQuery('#about-list').on('click', 'a', function(){
        var el = jQuery(this);

        Helper.logClickRecord({
          page: '122',
          recId: '12201x',
          objectType: 'article',
          zhandianId: '123372',
          objectId: el.parents('li').data('id'),
          alg: 'etrec',
          flags: el.parents('li').data('flag')
        })
      })

      // 曝光打点
      Helper.logExposureRecord({
        container: '#about-list',
        target: 'li',
        threshold: 0
      }, {
        ctr_type: '122',
        page_area: '12201',
        interface_id: '12201',
        object_type: 'article',
        l_offerid: articleId
      })
    }

    // 日排行榜
    function getAbout(){
      var articleId = jQuery('input[name="articleId"]').val();

      // 获取数据
      jQuery.ajax({
        type: 'get',
        url: '//osap.1688.com/home/Individual/getIndividualContentList.jsonp',
        data: {
          zhandian: 123372, // 开发：133224 线上：123372
          articleId: articleId,
          pageNum: 1
        },
        dataType: 'jsonp'
      }).then(function(result){

          if( result && result.success ){
            var content = result.content;

            if( content ){
              var dataList = content['valueObject'];
              var listTmpl = '{{if content}}'
                          +'{{each content as value i}}'
                            +'{{if i == 0 && value.maprow["thumbnailPic"] }}'
                              +'<li class="first-about" data-id="{{value.maprow.id}}" data-alg="etrec" data-flag="{{if value.maprow.isRecommend === true}}1{{else if value.maprow.isRecommend === false}}0{{/if}}">'
                                +'<a href="//toutiao.1688.com/article/{{value.maprow.id}}.htm" target="_blank" title="{{value.maprow.title}}">'
                                  +'<img src="{{value.maprow.thumbnailPic}}">'
                                  +'<div class="about-recommend-info">'
                                    +'<p class="about-recommend-title">{{value.maprow.title}}</p>'
                                    +'<div class="publish-info">'
                                      +'<span class="info-left">{{value.maprow.nickName}}</span>'
                                      +'<span class="info-right">{{value.maprow.publishtime | fommatPublishTime}}</span>'
                                    +'</div>'
                                  +'</div>'
                                +'</a>'
                              +'</li>'
                            +'{{else}}'
                              +'<li data-id="{{value.maprow.id}}" data-alg="etrec" data-flag="{{if value.maprow.isRecommend === true}}1{{else if value.maprow.isRecommend === false}}0{{/if}}">'
                                +'<a href="//toutiao.1688.com/article/{{value.maprow.id}}.htm" target="_blank" title="{{value.maprow.title}}">'
                                  +'{{value.maprow.title}}'
                                +'</a>'
                                  +'<div class="about-recommend-info">'
                                    +'<p class="about-recommend-title"></p>'
                                    +'<div class="publish-info">'
                                      +'<span class="info-left">{{value.maprow.nickName}}</span>'
                                      +'<span class="info-right">{{value.maprow.publishtime | fommatPublishTime}}</span>'
                                    +'</div>'
                                  +'</div>'
                                
                              +'</li>'
                            +'{{/if}}'
                            +'{{/each}}'
                          +'{{/if}}';

              var listRender = Template.compile( listTmpl );
              var $html = $( listRender({
                content: dataList
              }) );

              jQuery('#about-list').html( $html );
              // 打点
              logAboutRecord( articleId );
              return;
            }
          }

          jQuery('.toutiao-about').hide();
      })
    }
    getAbout();
})
</script>
